metadata.name: I see you
metadata.description:
Dark blu background, indigo colores are displayng the depth of a person's soul. It is a deep and not fully known as the universe.
The eyes  are a symbol of  the voices of souls, that give people the choose of their action, thoughts at any given time.
This art is telling about of conscience, openness and truth. That the truth is always stronger that anything in the world. The truth is the purity of consciousness.
It means "I see you", I see what you do".
This art is a reminder for all of us. 
The real size of oil painting 24 x 30
NFT 4025x5000   300dpi
